    "title": "Hekalu Kuu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "hekalu kuu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu alitaka watu waabudu mahali alipochagua kuweka jina lake. Kwa Waisraeli, hii ilikuwa kwanza ni hema na baadaye hekalu huko Yerusalemu.</p><p>Mungu ni <em>mtukufu </em>(juu ya vitu vyote) na <em>yupo kila mahali </em>(yupo kila mahali). Hata hivyo, alichagua mahali maalum kwa ajili ya Waisraeli kumwabudu. Mfalme Solomoni baadaye aliuliza jinsi Mungu wa mbinguni angeweza kuishi katika jengo lililojengwa na wanadamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:27\">1 Wafalme 8:27</a>). Jibu ni kwamba jina la Mungu linamwakilisha yeye mwenyewe.</p><p>Hema na baadaye hekalu vilikuwa mali yake na jina lake liliwatambulisha. Kwa hivyo, kwa namna fulani, vilikuwa nyumba zake. Katika Mashariki ya Karibu ya kale, majina yalikuwa zaidi ya lebo tu. Yalionyesha tabia na asili ya mtu (kwa mfano, Yakobo, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:36\">Mwanzo 27:36</a>; Yesu, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">Mathayo 1:21</a>; Barnaba, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:36\">Matendo 4:36</a>; Petro, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:17-Matt16:19\">Mathayo 16:17–19</a>). Hivyo, Solomoni angeweza kusema, “Jina zuri linapendeza zaidi kuliko utajiri mkubwa” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1\">Mithali 22:1</a>).</p><p>Mungu aliishi katika patakatifu lililobeba jina lake. Uwepo wake wa utukufu ulionekana kama moto na wingu wakati Waisraeli walipoishi nyikani. Hii ilitumika kama ukumbusho wa kudumu kwamba alikuwa pamoja na watu wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">Kutoka 40:34–35</a>). Vivyo hivyo, wakati Solomoni alipoanzisha hekalu, uwepo wa Mungu pia ulikuwa dhahiri (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1 Wafalme 8:10–11</a>).</p><p>Mungu baadaye aliishi kati ya watu wake kama Yesu Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">Yohana 1:14</a>). Hii iliondoa hitaji la patakatifu kuu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:19-John4:24\">Yohana 4:19–24</a>). Sasa, kwa kuwa Roho Mtakatifu anaishi ndani yao, Wakristo wote wanaweza &quot;kuweka&quot; uwepo wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1 Wakorintho 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">6:19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2 Wakorintho 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21\">Waefeso 2:21</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:8-Exod25:9\">Kutoka 25:8–9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:22\">22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:40\">40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:30\">26:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:7-Exod33:11\">33:7–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">40:34–35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:1\">Hesabu 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:16\">11:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:4-Deut12:7\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 12:4–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:14-Deut31:15\">31:14–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1 Wafalme 8:10–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:27\">27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">Yohana 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:19-John2:21\">2:19–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:44\">Matendo 7:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1 Wakorintho 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">6:19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2 Wakorintho 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21\">Waefeso 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:2\">Waebrania 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:5\">5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:22\">Ufunuo 21:22</a></p>",
